    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 76-77.</p><p>Strike of the Covenant</p><p>Prerequisite: Level 22+ Warlock, Thirsting Blade Invocation</p><p>The strength of your patron manifests in a single eldritch strike. You can use your action and expend 1 Legendary Point to perform a Strike of the Covenant. Make a single melee weapon attack against a creature within range, with the reach of your weapon increased to 30 feet. You have a +10 bonus to hit on this attack.</p><p>On a hit, the attack deals 10d8 x 5 radiant or necrotic damage (your choice) instead of your weapon’s normal damage. This attack does not benefit from any other bonus to its damage rolls. On a critical hit, you do not multiply the damage dice by 2, but instead deal 13d8 x 5 radiant or necrotic damage (your choice). You regain hit points equal to half the damage dealt.</p><p>Once you perform a Strike of the Covenant, you cannot do so again until you finish a short or long rest.</p></div>",
